Create the Dataset

To create a dataset, follow these steps:

In CRM Analytics, click Monitor > Jobs View > Dataflow View.
Click the actions list for the dataflow and select Download to download the existing dataflow definition file.
Open the dataflow definition file in a JSON or text editor.
Add the updated JSON.
Use a JSON validation tool to verify that the JSON is valid.
Save and close the dataflow definition file.
In CRM Analytics, click Monitor > Jobs View > Dataflow View.
Click the actions list for the dataflow and select Upload.
Select the updated dataflow definition file and click Upload.
Run the dataflow job by clicking Run.
